hosts_toggle - a host file swapper dashboard widget for OSX

Usage:
 * create two copies of your /etc/hosts files: /etc/hosts.orig and /etc/hosts.dev.
 * Adjust these as needed to define your hosts for normal and dev mode.
 * build the dashboard widget using dashcode
    - From the File menu, select Deploy, and from the menu shown, select "Delpoy to Dashboard."
